attorney%20general%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20and%20civil%20rights%20leader%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20Jr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20accordance%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20directive...%20all%20records%20previously%20withheld%20for%20classification%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Assassination%20Records%20Collection%20are%20released%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Archives%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20website%20Tuesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Archives%20has%20released%20millions%20of%20pages%20of%20records%20over%20the%20past%20decades%20relating%20to%20the%20assassination%20of%20then-president%20Kennedy%20in%20November%201963%2C%20but%20thousands%20of%20documents%20had%20been%20held%20back%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency%20and%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Warren%20Commission%20that%20investigated%20the%20shooting%20of%20the%20charismatic%2046-year-old%20president%20determined%20that%20it%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20former%20Marine%20sharpshooter%2C%20Lee%20Harvey%20Oswald%2C%20acting%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20formal%20conclusion%20has%20done%20little%20to%20quell%20speculation%20that%20a%20more%20sinister%20plot%20was%20behind%20Kennedy's%20murder%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20the%20slow%20release%20of%20the%20government%20files%20has%20added%20fuel%20to%20various%20conspiracy%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKennedy%20scholars%20have%20said%20the%20documents%20that%20were%20still%20held%20by%20the%20archives%20were%20unlikely%20to%20contain%20any%20bombshell%20revelations%20or%20put%20to%20rest%20the%20rampant%20conspiracy%20theories%20about%20the%20assassination%20of%20the%2035th%20US%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOswald%20was%20shot%20by%20a%20strip%20club%20owner%2C%20Jack%20Ruby%2C%20on%20November%2024%2C%201963%20--%20two%20days%20after%20the%20Kennedy%20assassination%20--%20while%20being%20moved%20to%20a%20county%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20records%20already%20released%20were%20raw%20intelligence%2C%20including%20scores%20of%20reports%20from%20FBI%20agents%20following%20up%20leads%20that%20led%20nowhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20what%20they%20contain%20was%20also%20previously%20known%2C%20such%20as%20that%20the%20communist-obsessed%20CIA%20cooked%20up%20several%20outlandish%20plots%20to%20murder%20Cuba's%20Fidel%20Castro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOswald%20defected%20to%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%201959%20but%20returned%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%201962.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20books%20and%20movies%20such%20as%20the%201991%20Oliver%20Stone%20film%20%26quot%3BJFK%26quot%3B%20have%20fueled%20the%20conspiracy%20industry%2C%20pointing%20the%20finger%20at%20Cold%20War%20rivals%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20or%20Cuba%2C%20the%20Mafia%20and%20even%20Kennedy's%20vice%20president%2C%20Lyndon%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20documents%20follows%20an%20October%2026%2C%201992%20act%20of%20Congress%20which%20required%20that%20the%20unredacted%20assassination%20records%20held%20in%20the%20National%20Archives%20be%20released%20in%20full%2025%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742345040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-10%2Fjohn-f-kennedy-jfk-file-photo_650x400_81508598502.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-releases-final-trove-of-secret-john-f-kennedy-assassination-files-7955807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20National%20Archives%20on%20Tuesday%20released%20the%20final%20batch%20of%20files%20related%20to%20the%20November%201963%20assassination%20of%20president%20J