alth%20and%20Human%20Services%20is%20responsible%20for%20promoting%20the%20health%20of%20Americans.%20Among%20the%20largest%20agencies%20in%20HHS%20are%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20preventing%20diseases%2C%20the%20FDA%2C%20which%20ensures%20the%20safety%20of%20food%20and%20drugs%2C%20and%20the%20Centers%20for%20Medicare%20%26amp%3B%20Medicaid%20Services%2C%20which%20oversees%20Medicare%20and%20helps%20administer%20the%20federal%20portion%20of%20Medicaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22acb4cc5c-c298-4b7c-9ecb-f1415154fb46%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVeterans%20Affairs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs%20terminated%201%2C900%20of%20roughly%2046%2C000%20probationary%20employees.%20After%20a%20review%2C%20this%20was%20narrowed%20down%20to%201%2C683%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VA%20said%20it%20continues%20to%20try%20to%20notify%20those%201%2C683%20employees%20of%20their%20reinstatement%20but%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20reach%20all%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Veterans%20Affairs%20Department%20is%20the%20second-largest%20Cabinet%20agency.%20It%20is%20responsible%20for%20healthcare%20and%20other%20services%20to%20veterans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243ed901a-d1a4-48fd-b75e-ef290730b98a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterior%20Department%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Interior%20terminated%201%2C712%20employees%2C%20including%201%2C303%20probationary%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Interior%20Department%20said%20it%20has%20canceled%20terminations%20for%20roughly%2090%25%20of%20the%201%2C710%20employees%20terminated%20during%20their%20probationary%20or%20trial%20period.%20The%20department%20said%20it%20will%20not%20reinstate%20two%20employees%20who%20are%20covered%20by%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Interior%20Department%20manages%20public%20lands%20both%20through%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Land%20Management%2C%20which%20awards%20commercial%20leases%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Parks%20Service%2C%20which%20manages%20national%20parks%20and%20many%20national%20monuments%20and%20historic%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e301da8-8d7a-470c-a7cd-d7bebb0eeedd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommerce%20Department%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20terminated%20791%20of%20roughly%209%2C000%20total%20probationary%20or%20trial%20period%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%2027%20employees%20were%20reinstated%20within%20days%20of%20firing%20%26quot%3Bfor%20various%20operational%20reasons.%26quot%3B%20The%20department%20said%20it%20had%20notified%20the%20other%20764%20employees%20of%20their%20reinstatement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Commerce%20Department%20helps%20promote%20economic%20growth%20and%20includes%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20agencies%2C%20from%20the%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%20to%20the%20Census%20Bureau%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20planning%20and%20administering%20the%20once-a-decade%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22365d8620-edd3-48d3-ab82-6b150b7c2bea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransportation%20Department%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20filing%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20terminated%20788%20probationary%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20only%20775%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20court%20order.%20The%20remaining%20employees%20were%20either%20fired%20for%20performance%20reasons%20(2)%2C%20already%20had%20their%20terminations%20rescinded%20(8)%2C%20resigned%20(2)%2C%20or%20accepted%20a%20deferred%20resignation%20program%20(1).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20775%20employees%20have%20all%20been%20notified%20of%20their%20reinstatement.%20The%20department%20said%20it%20would%20place%20all%20affected%20workers%20on%20leave%20through%20March%2019%20to%20allow%20time%20to%20coordinate%20their%20return%2C%20including%20returning%20government%20equipment%20and%20issuing%20new%20ID%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Transportation%20Department%20is%20responsible%20for%20managing%20the%20nation's%20transportation%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20agencies%20like%20the%20FAA%20and%20Federal%20Highway%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e66c7ed-dd47-4e48-87fc-bcb014a93e8c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnergy%20Department%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Energy%20terminated%20555%20probationary%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20it%20had%20canceled%20the%20termination%20of%20all%20of%20the%20affected%20employees%20and%20placed%20them%20on%20retroactive%20leave%20until%20their%20badging%20and%20IT%20status%20are%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Energy%20Department%20is%20responsible%20for%20national%20energy%20policy%20and%20maintaining%20the%20US'%20nuclear%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20the%20security%20of%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279b68971-249f-42b6-9cfa-c0f498433f18%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnvironmental%20Protection%20Agency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EPA%20terminated%20roughly%20419%20probationary%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20it%20has%20notified%20all%20of%20the%20affected%20employees%20of%20their%20reinstatement.%20Most%20of%20the%20419%20workers%20have%20been%20put%20on%20paid%20leave%2C%20though%20some%20(%26quot%3Bincluding%20students%20on%20leave%20for%20the%20school%20year%26quot%3B)%20are%20on%20unpaid%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreated%20in%201970%2C%20the%20EPA%20is%20responsible%20for%20enforcing%20environmental%20laws.%20The%20agency%20says%20it%20makes%20sure%20Americans%20have%20clean%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245021813-17af-4b5f-b8f9-436d02cf56cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeneral%20Services%20Administration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GSA%20has%20terminated%20roughly%20366%20of%20approximately%20812%20probationary%20and%20trial%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Monday%20morning%2C%20the%20GSA%20said%20it%20had%20reinstated%20all%20employees%2C%20minus%20two%20who%20declined%20to%20return%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%20called%20the%20federal%20government's%20landlord%2C%20the%20GSA%20helps%20the%20federal%20government%20manage%20contracting%20for%20goods%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22996fd3c7-a544-4552-8584-a6ce1d2b9fe0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHomeland%20Security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20terminated%20at%20least%20313%20probationary%20employees.%20The%20department%20did%20not%20indicate%20the%20number%20of%20total%20probationary%20workers%20it%20terminated%20because%20it%20said%20those%20fired%20for%20performance%20or%20conduct%20issues%20were%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDHS%20said%20it%20has%20begun%20the%20process%20of%20reinstating%20more%20than%20310%20workers.%20One%20employee%20declined%20to%20return%2C%20while%20another%20worker%20was%20already%20in%20the%20process%20of%20coming%20back%20due%20to%20a%20deferred%20resignation%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202001%2C%20DHS%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20the%20third-largest%20Cabinet%20agency%20%E2%80%94%20it%20encompasses%20everything%20from%20the%20Transportation%20Security%20Administration%20and%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20to%20the%20Secret%20Service%20and%20the%20Federal%20Emergency%20Management%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201bcf6e8-c37a-4b0f-b9db-7c21d9e99c17%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHousing%20and%20Urban%20Development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development%20(HUD)%20terminated%20312%20of%20roughly%20549%20probationary%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHUD%20said%20it%20has%20fully%20reinstated%2013%20employees.%20The%20department%20said%20it%20has%20begun%20the%20reinstatement%20process%20for%20the%20remaining%20workers%20who%20are%20being%20placed%20on%20administrative%20leave%20temporarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development%20is%20responsible%20for%20addressing%20housing%20policy%20and%20enforcing%20fair%20housing%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec89aa1c-0e48-4de1-bcc6-5a49574825ec%5C%22%3ESmall%20Business%20Administration%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Small%20Business%20Administration%20(SBA)%20terminated%20304%20of%20roughly%20700%20probationary%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SBA%20said%20it%20quickly%20rehired%20six%20workers%2C%20five%20of%20which%20remain%20with%20the%20agency.%20One%20employee%20resigned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20remaining%20employees%2C%20SBA%20said%20had%20notified%20all%20298%20workers%20of%20their%20reinstatement.%20The%20agency%20said%20127%20workers%20have%20been%20reinstated%20and%20put%20on%20paid%20leave.%20Employees%20who%20were%20on%20intermittent%20status%20(164)%20have%20been%20put%20into%20non-pay%20status%20and%20will%20not%20receive%20back%20pay%20due%20to%20their%20work%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Small%20Business%20Administration%20is%20a%20Cabinet-level%20agency%20focused%20on%20helping%20small%20business%20owners%20and%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254d55970-38cc-4fcb-bfe6-6467dad3642a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUSAID%20terminated%20270%20of%20295%20probationary%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSAID%20says%20it%20has%20notified%20the%20affected%20workers%20of%20their%20reinstatement.%20If%20they%20return%20to%20work%2C%20they%20will%20be%20placed%20on%20administrative%20leave%20until%20further%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20aid%20agency%2C%20which%20had%20operations%20worldwide%2C%20is%20different%20from%20the%20other%2017%20departments%20and%20agencies%20covered%20by%20the%20order%20in%20that%20it%20has%20already%20effectively%20begun%20to%20shut%20down%20its%20operations.%20USAID%20previously%20vacated%20its%20