%20that%20are%20from%20when%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20that%20are%20full%20of%20dark%2C%20weird%20stories%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Brien%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20CR%20cofounder-written%20book%20is%20%26quot%3BSmiley%20Day%3A%20A%20Good%20Advice%20Book%20From%20Your%20Favorite%20Robot%20Therapist%2C%26quot%3B%20by%20CR%20cofounder%20Sam%20Riegel.%20It%20will%20be%20released%20on%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20a%20parent%2C%20you%20read%20a%20lot%20of%20children's%20books%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20of%20'em%20are%20great%2C%20and%20some%20of%20'em%20were%20not%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Riegel%2C%20a%20father%20of%20two%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20thought%2C%20'Maybe%20we%20should%20try%20to%20make%20a%20good%20one.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a87a19a-1964-4f82-97b5-516cc3382dcd%5C%22%3EMore%20D%26amp%3BD-based%20novels%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECR%20has%20partnered%20with%20authors%20under%20the%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20stable%20to%20roll%20out%20novels%20based%20on%20their%20%26quot%3BD%26amp%3BD%26quot%3B%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20early%20title%20released%20in%202021%20under%20this%20collaboration%20was%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EVox%20Machina%20%E2%80%94%20Kith%20%26amp%3B%20Kin%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20novel-length%20deep%20dive%20into%20the%20backstories%20of%20the%20half-elven%20twins%20O'Brien%20and%20CR%20cofounder%20Laura%20Bailey%20played%20on%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20slate%20for%202025%20includes%20%26quot%3BTusk%20Love%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20novel%20by%20Thea%20Guanzon%2C%20inspired%20by%20characters%20in%20CR's%20second%20long-running%20campaign.%20And%20there's%20a%20short%20story%20collection%20with%20a%20foreword%20from%20O'Brien%2C%20%26quot%3BVox%20Machina%20%E2%80%94%20Stories%20Untold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20team%20at%20Critical%20Role%20is%20incredible%20at%20telling%20stories%2C%20so%20it%20just%20made%20sense%20to%20expand%20those%20stories%20into%20books%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elizabeth%20Schaefer%2C%20the%20publishing%20director%20at%20Random%20House%20Worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20setting%20and%20characters%20are%20so%20rich%20that%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20publish%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20books%E2%80%94from%20novels%20to%20a%20cookbook%2C%20to%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20making%20of%2C%20to%20even%20an%20advice%20book%2C%26quot%3B%20Schaefer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Brien%20joked%20that%20he%20ended%20up%20taking%20charge%20of%20CR's%20literary%20offerings%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20others%20are%20too%20busy%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20all%20worked%20out%20since%20he%20loves%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20part%20of%20the%20team's%20publishing%20drive%2C%20it's%20O'Brien's%20job%20to%20curate%20CR's%20art%20books.%20He%20also%20consults%20on%20the%20company's%20graphic%20novel%20collaborations%20with%20Dark%20Horse%20Comics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20an%20avid%20reader%2C%20and%20my%20slippery%20slide%20into%20tabletop%20role-playing%20games%20and%20fantasy%20was%20through%20reading%20novels%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Brien%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20really%2C%20my%20whole%20life%20has%20been%20about%20being%20a%20big%20nerd%20and%20then%20deciding%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20an%20adult%20now%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20realizing%20that%20that%20was%20incorrect%20and%20then%20just%20fusing%20it%20all%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-book-publishing-expansion-liam-obrien-cofounder-novels-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742342881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d25387b8b41a9673fa7e09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-book-publishing-expansion-liam-obrien-cofounder-n