.com%2Fpeanut-is-tinder-but-for-moms-and-it-just-launched-in-san-francisco-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeanut%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20magazine%20when%20my%20son%20was%20an%20infant.%20I%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20connecting%20with%20other%20women%20in%20the%20same%20situation%20as%20me%20and%20eagerly%20started%20using%20the%20app%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-only-friend-baby-helped-meet-new-people-mom-friends-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeetups%20%3C%2Fa%3Eonce%20my%20son%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20run%20around%20and%20play.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESince%20Peanut%20is%20geared%20towards%20women%2C%20it%20works%20well%20both%20for%20arranging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbackyard-hangout-spot-neighborhood-kids-simple-play-rules-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaydates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20making%20friends%20for%20myself.%20The%20app%20is%20set%20up%20similarly%20to%20online%20dating%2C%20users%20create%20a%20profile%2C%20check%20some%20boxes%20with%20your%20interests%20like%20%26quot%3Bbookworm%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bgamer%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20list%20your%20kids'%20ages%2C%20and%20then%20swipe%20through%20profile%20matches.%20The%20app%20allows%20users%20to%20customize%20the%20experience%2C%20by%20showing%20potential%20connections%20based%20on%20location%20and%20child's%20age%2C%20as%20well%20as%20interests%20or%20work%20life.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20completed%20the%20initial%20signup%2C%20I%20heard%20back%20from%20my%20first%20connections%20within%201%20to%202%20days.%20I%20chatted%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20a%20few%20of%20them%20for%20several%20weeks%20before%20suggesting%20a%20meetup.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20first%20mom%20I%20agreed%20to%20meet%20up%20with%20invited%20another%20Peanut%20connection%20on%20the%20same%20zoo%20outing.%20All%20three%20of%20us%20had%20sons%20who%20were%20around%20the%20same%20age.%20While%20at%20the%20z