cleshow%2F119178423.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNegotiations%20With%20Hamas%20Will%20Take%20Place%20Only%20Under%20Fire%26quot%3B%3A%20Netanyahu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20warned%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20massive%20overnight%20strikes%20on%20Gaza%20were%20%26quot%3Bonly%20the%20beginning%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20future%20negotiations%20with%20Hamas%20%26quot%3Bwill%20take%20place%20only%20under%20fire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%2C%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20since%20a%20truce%20took%20effect%20in%20January%2C%20killed%20more%20than%20400%20people%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20according%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20%26quot%3BHamas%20has%20already%20felt%20the%20strength%20of%20our%20arm%20in%20the%20past%2024%20hours.%20And%20I%20want%20to%20promise%20you%20%E2%80%93-%20and%20them%20%E2%80%93-%20this%20is%20only%20the%20beginning%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENegotiations%20have%20stalled%20over%20how%20to%20proceed%20with%20a%20ceasefire%20whose%20first%20phase%20has%20expired%2C%20with%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20disagreeing%20on%20whether%20to%20move%20to%20a%20new%20phase%20intended%20to%20bring%20the%20war%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20premier%20said%20in%20his%20address%20that%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20now%20on%2C%20negotiations%20will%20take%20place%20only%20under%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20before%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BMilitary%20pressure%20is%20essential%20for%20the%20release%20of%20additional%20hostages%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20keep%20fighting%20until%20the%20return%20of%20all%20the%20hostages%20seized%20by%20Palestinian%20militants%20during%20the%20October%202023%20attack%20that%20sparked%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%20witnesses%20in%20Gaza%20said%20the%20attacks%20had%20largely%20stopped%2C%20though%20sporadic%20bombing%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20I%20felt%20that%20Gaza%20is%20a%20real%20hell%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jihan%20Nahhal%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20woman%20from%20Gaza%20City%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20of%20her%20relatives%20were%20wounded%20or%20killed%20in%20the%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuddenly%20there%20were%20huge%20explosions%2C%20as%20if%20it%20were%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20which%20has%20not%20responded%20militarily%20so%20far%2C%20accused%20Israel%20of%20attempting%20to%20force%20it%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20Israel%20consulted%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20before%20launching%20the%20strikes%2C%20while%20Israel%20said%20the%20return%20to%20fighting%20was%20%26quot%3Bfully%20coordinated%26quot%3B%20with%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BHamas%20bears%20total%20responsibility...%20for%20the%20resumption%20of%20hostilities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hamas%20statement%20later%20urged%20friendly%20countries%20to%20%26quot%3Bpressure%26quot%3B%20the%20United%20States%20to%20bring%20to%20an%20end%20the%20strikes%20by%20its%20ally%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20and%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20condemned%20the%20strikes%2C%20while%20the%20families%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20pleaded%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20to%20halt%20the%20violence%2C%20fearing%20for%20the%20fate%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Complete%20destruction'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20office%20said%20Tuesday's%20operation%20was%20ordered%20after%20%26quot%3BHamas's%20repeated%20refusal%20to%20release%20our%20hostages%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20Israel%20had%20%26quot%3Bdecided%20to%20overturn%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%26quot%3B%20brokered%20by%20US%2C%20Qatari%20and%20Egyptian%20mediators%2C%20and%20warned%20that%20the%20resumption%20of%20violence%20would%20%26quot%3Bimpose%20a%20death%20sentence%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20remaining%20living%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20leader%2C%20Sami%20Abu%20Zuhri%2C%20told%20AFP%20the%20aim%20of%20the%20strikes%20was%20%26quot%3Bto%20impose%20a%20surrender%20agreement%2C%20writing%20it%20in%20the%20blood%20of%20Gaza%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BHamas%20must%20understand%20that%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20have%20changed%26quot%3B%2C%20threatening%20to%20unleash%20the%20Israeli%20military%20until%20the%20group's%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20destruction%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20did%20not%20immediately%20free%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20the%20head%20of%20its%20government%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Essam%20al-Dalis%2C%20was%20among%20several%20officials%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20AFP%20footage%20showed%20people%20rushing%20wounded%20people%20on%20stretchers%2C%20including%20young%20children%2C%20to%20hospital.%20Bodies%20covered%20with%20white%20shrouds%20were%20also%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital's%20mortuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Shocking'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%20the%20bodies%20of%20413%20people%20had%20been%20received%20by%20hospitals%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Ba%20number%20of%20victims%20are%20still%20under%20the%20rubble%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNICEF%20spokeswoman%20Rosalia%20Bollen%2C%20speaking%20to%20AFP%20in%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20said%20the%20deaths%20include%20%26quot%3Bdozens%20and%20dozens%20of%20children%2C%20with%20many%20more%20children%20wounded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20facilities%20that%20%26quot%3Bhave%20already%20been%20decimated%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20war%20were%20now%20%26quot%3Boverwhelmed%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamilies%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20rallied%20in%20front%20of%20Netanyahu's%20office%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20and%20a%20campaign%20group%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20causing%20%26quot%3Bthe%20explosion%20of%20the%20ceasefire%2C%20which%20could%20sacrifice%20their%20family%20members%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernments%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Europe%20and%20elsewhere%20called%20for%20the%20renewed%20hostilities%20to%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20images%20of%20burning%20tents%20in%20refugee%20camps%20are%20shocking.%20Fleeing%20children%20and%20internally%20displaced%20persons%20must%20never%20be%20used%20as%20leverage%20in%20negotiations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Germany's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Annalena%20Baerbock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20backer%20Iran%20denounced%20the%20wave%20of%20attacks%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontinuation%20of%20the%20genocide%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%2C%20while%20Russia%20and%20China%20warned%20against%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEgyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20said%20the%20strikes%20were%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20efforts%20to%20make%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20uninhabitable%20and%20force%20the%20Palestinians%20into%20displacement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20floated%20a%20proposal%20to%20move%20Palestinians%20out%20of%20Gaza%2C%20an%20idea%20that%20was%20rejected%20by%20Palestinians%20and%20governments%20in%20the%20region%20and%20beyond%2C%20but%20embraced%20by%20some%20Israeli%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20wave%20of%20strikes%20began%2C%20Netanyahu's%20Likud%20movement%20said%20that%20a%20far-right%20party%20that%20had%20quit%20the%20government%20in%20January%20in%20protest%20at%20the%20Gaza%20truce%20would%20rejoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Attack%20from%20Yemen%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaz