ions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cahn%20recommends%20using%20non-clumping%20litter%20for%20kittens%20who%20may%20accidentally%20ingest%20litter%20while%20exploring%20their%20surroundings.%20If%20your%20adult%20cat%20eats%20litter%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20consult%20your%20veterinarian%2C%20as%20it%20could%20indicate%20an%20underlying%20medical%20condition.%20While%20rare%2C%20Cahn%20says%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%20is%20that%20a%20cat%20ingests%20enough%20clumping%20litter%20for%20it%20to%20bind%20together%20in%20the%20digestive%20tract%20and%20cause%20a%20blockage%20that%20may%20require%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3026491-6767-4415-aabf-5bef5df6d58c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Non-clumping%20cat%20litter%20cons%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENon-clumping%20cat%20litter%20cons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifficult%20to%20remove%20liquid%20waste%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20means%20your%20cat%20may%20have%20to%20step%20on%20soiled%20litter%20to%20eliminate%2C%20and%20the%20lingering%20urine%20can%20produce%20an%20ammonia%20odor.%20%26quot%3BThe%20increased%20odor%20associated%20with%20urine%20being%20mixed%20into%20the%20box%20may%20be%20enough%20to%20make%20a%20cat%20not%20want%20to%20use%20the%20box%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20is%20not%20cleaned%20frequently%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahn%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECostly%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20some%20people%20see%20the%20lack%20of%20scooping%20clumps%20as%20an%20advantage%20of%20non-clumping%20litter%2C%20the%20downside%20is%20that%20the%20entire%20box%20usually%20needs%20to%20be%20emptied%20and%20refilled%20at%20least%20weekly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETexture%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20cat%20litter%2C%20there's%20no%20one-size-fits-all%20solution%2C%20especially%20with%20pellets.%20Delgado%20generally%20doesn't%20recommend%20pellet%20litters%20because%20their%20larger%2C%20harder%20texture%20can%20be%20uncomfortable%20for%20cats%20to%20stand%20and%20dig%20in%2C%20causing%20some%20to%20avoid%20the%20litter%20box%20altogether.%20This%20is%20often%20the%20case%20with%20wooden%20pellet%20litters%2C%20a%20popular%20non-clumping%20option.%20However%2C%20not%20all%20pellets%20are%20the%20same.%20We%20liked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74876-20%26h%3Dfa3aa97d214769e77889c3946d36f505b819b249e3e0b807362408ccdd9c8308%26postID%3D67d99499e45285883912df55%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fclumping-vs-non-clumping-litter%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fokocat-dust-free-unscented-non%252Fdp%252F929854%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C3%96kocat's%20Non-Clumping%20Paper%20Pellet%20Litter%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20its%20smaller%2C%20softer%20pellets%20were%20the%20most%20absorbent%20of%20all%20the%20paper%20litters%20we%20tested%20and%20produced%20almost%20no%20dust.%20Ultimately%2C%20finding%20the%20right%20texture%20is%20about%20what%20works%20best%20for%20your%20cat's%20comfort%20and%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228bd7b679-28b3-4221-86dd-38e251c1c9c7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Clumping%20vs.%20non-clumping%20litter%3A%20Which%20is%20better%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EClumping%20vs.%20non-clumping%20litter%3A%20Which%20is%20better%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20clumping%20and%20non-clumping%20litter%20come%20in%20budget%20and%20premium%20options%2C%20so%20their%20prices%20are%20generally%20similar.%20However%2C%20clumping%20litter%20typically%20lasts%20longer%2C%20offering%20better%20value%20for%20your%20money.%20And%20if%20sustainability%20is%20important%20to%20you%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-natural-cat-litter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20natural%20cat%20litter%3C%2Fa%3E%20options%20we%20tested%20are%20available%20in%20both%20clumping%20and%20non-clumping%20varieties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20non-clumping%20litter%20absorbs%20moisture%20and%20controls%20odors%2C%20the%20experts%20we%20spoke%20with%20agree%20that%20clumping%20litter%20is%20generally%20the%20better%20option%20for%20odor%20control%20and%20hygiene.%20It%20locks%20in%20liquids%2C%20forms%20solid%20clumps%20for%20easy%20scooping%2C%20and%20encourages%20cats%20to%20dig%20and%20bury%20their%20waste.%20However%2C%20some%20clumping%20litters%20can%20be%20dusty%2C%20which%20may%20be%20a%20concern%20for%20cats%20with%20respiratory%20issues.%20Non-clumping%20litter%20might%20be%20a%20better%20choice%20for%20kittens%20or%20long-haired%20cats%2C%20but%20it%20typically%20requires%20more%20frequent%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20bringing%20home%20a%20new%20cat%20or%20kitten%2C%20try%20to%20find%20out%20what%20litter%20they've%20been%20using%20and%20stick%20with%20it%20if%20possible%2C%20Cahn%20says.%20But%20if%20you're%20starting%20from%20scratch%2C%20Delgado%20has%20a%20simple%20recommendation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20go%20wrong%20starting%20with%20a%20soft%2C%20sandy%2C%20unscented%20clumping%20style%20litter%20because%20this%20is%20what%20most%20cats%20prefer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20still%20not%20sure%20whether%20clumping%20or%20non-clumping%20litter%20is%20better%20for%20your%20cat%2C%20consider%20the%20key%20benefits%20of%20each%20type.%20Clumping%20litter%20may%20be%20best%20for%20multi-cat%20households%2C%20cost%20savings%2C%20efficient%20cleanup%2C%20and%20cats%20who%20prefer%20fine%2C%20sand-like%20textures.%20Non-clumping%20litter%20may%20be%20best%20for%20kittens%2C%20long-haired%20cats%2C%20and%20cats%20with%20respiratory%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a111153e-1f0b-4408-a568-1776cf3a9c8d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20most%20often%20recommend%20clumping%20cat%20litter.%20Its%20ease%20of%20scooping%20and%20better%20odor%20contr