e%20this%20can%20help%20parents%20return%20to%20work%20with%20ease.%20Plus%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20most%20of%20our%20paychecks%20on%20childcare.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESweden's%20flexible%20parental%20leave%20policies%20also%20provide%3C%2Fspan%3E%20480%20days%20of%20paid%20leave%20(about%20240%20days%20per%20parent)%20when%20a%20child%20is%20born%20or%20adopted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20paid%20leave%20this%20long%20that%20also%20includes%20fathers%20is%20rare%20to%20find%20around%20the%20world.%20It%3Cspan%3E%20meant%20I%20was%20able%20to%20spend%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20time%20bonding%20with%20my%20daughter%20when%20she%20was%20little%2C%20which%20was%20amazing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22215235ba-8fd9-4597-a5d5-e971f96489c0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20country%20offers%20unhindered%20access%20to%20dramatic%20natural%20beauty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Skule%20mountain%2C%20high%20coast%20in%20Sweden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1ca6369253ccddf990744%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESweden%20has%20mountains%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20more.%20%3Cp%3EBj%C3%B6rn%20Forenius%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20draws%20is%20Sweden's%20raw%20natural%20beauty%20%E2%80%94%20pristine%20forests%2C%20dramatic%20mountains%2C%20and%20wild%20skies.%20I%20can%20sometimes%20see%20the%20northern%20lights%20from%20my%20living%20room!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20an%20abundance%20of%20nature%20just%2015%20minutes%20outside%20Stockholm%2C%20but%20one%20of%20my%20highlights%20came%20during%20a%20week%20in%20The%20High%20Coast%2C%20around%20five%20hours%20north%20of%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20286%20meters%20above%20sea%20level%2C%20it's%20widely%20considered