nacks%2C%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22589de04a-470c-4000-ad7d-a537b85c065c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20seasons%20are%20clearly%20defined%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20the%20weather%20is%20very%20unpredictable%2C%20I%20instantly%20loved%20the%20seasonality%20in%20Sweden.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESummers%20tend%20to%20be%20consistently%20warm%20and%20dry%2C%20which%20is%20perfect%20weather%20for%20exploring%20nature.%20Then%20it's%20very%20cold%20and%20snowy%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20which%20really%20enhances%20the%20Christmas%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20summer%20can%20take%20a%20while%20to%20arrive.%20Swedes%20have%20a%20joke%20that%20after%20winter%2C%20you%20have%20the%20second%20winter%2C%20the%20third%20winter%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20then%20the%20fourth.%20Then%20it's%20instantly%20summer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20don't%20really%20get%20a%20spring%20or%20fall%20quite%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20the%20UK.%20But%20there's%20a%20clear%20separation%20between%20the%20seasons%2C%20and%20that%20allows%20us%20to%20fully%20embrace%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220272bfb7-b494-4634-b36a-71b32d059b42%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%A6%20but%20the%20winter%20darkness%20can%20feel%20endless%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224362%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dark%20blue%20skies%20in%20Sweden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1a6f4585f1dff88b1e396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223311%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20hadn't%20expected%20just%20how%20much%20longer%20limited%20daylight%20could%20make%20winter%20feel.%3Cp%3EDace%20Znotina%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20brings%20me%20to%20the%20one%20part%20of%20Swedish%20living%20that%20shows%20I'm%20not%20yet%20a%20true%20Scandinavian%3A%20I%20struggle%20with%20the%20oppressive%20darkness%20during%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Sweden%2C%20winter%20means%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshorter-days-health-mood-effects-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efewer%20hours%20of%20daylight%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20December%20in%20January.%20%3C%2Fspan%3ESome%20winter%20days%2C%20we're%20lucky%20to%20get%20just%20five%20hours%20of%20daylight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20mind%20the%20cold%20weather%2C%20but%20the%20darkness%20definitely%20affects%20me%20in%20a%20way%20I%20didn't%20anticipate.%20My%20mood%20feels%20lower%2C%20and%20my%20world%20a%20bit%20smaller.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227cf045d-314d-4bae-a485-b7e120e2dbc0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbove%20all%2C%20I%20think%20Sweden%20has%20the%20best%20capital%20city%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20lived%20in%20London%20for%2010%20years%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20love%20living%20in%20a%20big%20city.%20However%2C%20Stockholm%20is%20my%20favorite.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20truly%20beautiful%20city%20with%20brightly%20colored%20buildings%20in%20Gamla%20Stan%20and%20other%20historic%20areas%20that%20really%20give%20it%20warmth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20all%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20major%20capital%20city%20but%20still%20has%20something%20of%20a%20small-town%20vibe.%20It%20is%20walkable%20and%20has%20the%20best%20baked%20goods%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20nothing%20beats%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffabrique-swedish-cardamom-bun-taking-new-york-city-by-storm-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScandinavian%20bakery%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20archipelago%2C%20Stockholm%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20islands%2C%20so%20you're%20always%20near%20the%20water%20and%20can%20t