e%20war%20broke%20out%20and%20said%20due%20to%20the%20policy%20that%20was%20adopted%2C%20the%20country%20is%20now%20in%20a%20position%20where%20it%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20to%20lasting%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20had%20criticised%20India's%20stance%20when%20Russia%20attacked%20Ukraine%20and%20called%20for%20condemnation%20of%20the%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interactive%20session%20at%20the%20Raisina%20Dialogue%20here%2C%20the%20former%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20external%20affairs%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20wiping%20the%20egg%20of%20my%20face%20because%20I%20am%20one%20person%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20debate%20who%20actually%20criticised%20the%20Indian%20position%20at%20the%20time%20back%20in%20February%202022.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Thiruvananthapuram%20MP%20said%20his%20criticism%20was%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bwell-known%20grounds%20that%20there%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20UN%20charter%2C%20there%20had%20been%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20inviolability%20of%20borders%2C%20of%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20a%20member%20state%20namely%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20we%20had%20always%20stood%20for%20the%20inadmissibility%20of%20the%20use%20of%20force%20to%20settle%20international%20disputes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20those%20principles%20had%20been%20violated%20by%20one%20party%20and%20we%20should%20have%20condemned%20it.%20Well%2C%20three%20years%20later%20it%20does%20look%20like%20I%20am%20the%20one%20with%20the%20egg%20on%20my%20face%20because%20clearly%20the%20policy%20has%20meant%20that%20India%20actually%20has%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20can%20hug%20both%20the%20president%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20president%20in%20Moscow%20two%20weeks%20apart%20and%20be%20accepted%20in%20both%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20session%20titled%20'Waging%20Peace%3A%20Looking%20Back%20to%20Look%20Ahead'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20India%20is%20in%20a%20position%20where%20it%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20to%20a%20lasting%20peace%20if%20it%20was%20so%20required%20in%20ways%20that%20very%20few%20countries%20would%20be%20able%20to%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20benefits%20due%20to%20a%20number%20of%20factors%20including%20its%20distance%20from%20Europe%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20caveat%20that%20he%20cannot%20speak%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20government%20as%20he%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20also%20said%20if%20it%20were%20necessary%20and%20if%20there%20was%20an%20agreed%20peace%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20there%20would%20be%20some%20willingness%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20to%20consider%20sending%20peacekeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20Russians%20have%20made%20it%20explicit%20that%20they%20will%20not%20accept%20European%20peacekeepers%20who%20belong%20to%20NATO%20countries%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%20one%20would%20have%20to%20look%20beyond%20Europe%20for%20peacekeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpeaking%20as%20an%20Indian%20parliamentarian%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20resistance%20to%20that%20idea.%20There%20was%20resistance%20famously%20when%20there%20was%20a%20request%20in%202003%20for%20India%20to%20send%20troops%20to%20Iraq%20and%20Parliament%20got%20together%20and%20passed%20a%20resolution%2C%20saying%20that%20in%20no%20circumstance%2C%20will%20Indian%20peacekeepers%20go%20to%20Iraq%20after%20the%20American%20invasion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20MP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20that%20happening%20for%20Ukraine.%20I%20think%20if%20it%20were%20necessary%20and%20there%20was%20an%20agreed%20peace%2C%20I%20think%20there%20would%20be%20some%20willingness%20to%20consider.%20But%20I%20can't%20speak%20for%20the%20government%2C%20I%20am%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20said%20that%20wi