2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0the%20US%20President%20had%20said%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20nations%20are%20worried%20that%20President%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20not%20hidden%20his%20admiration%20for%20Russia's%20Putin%2C%20may%20agree%20to%20cede%20too%20much%20Ukrainian%20territory%20to%20Russia.%20They%20are%20also%20very%20concerned%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20not%20being%20consulted%20on%20decisions%20that%20may%20be%20agreed%20upon%20in%20today's%20phonecall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Zelensky's%20Oval%20Office%20showdown%20with%20President%20Trump%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20agreed%20to%20temporarily%20stop%20the%20war%20for%2030%20days%20and%20engage%20in%20dailogue%20with%20Russia%2C%20but%20President%20Putin%20has%20set%20a%20string%20of%20conditions%2C%20which%20Moscow%20has%20said%20is%20non-negotiable.%20And%20only%20if%20these%20guarantees%20can%20be%20provided%2C%20will%20Moscow%20and%20Kyiv%20sit%20for%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERejecting%20a%20barrage%20of%20conditions%20set%20by%20Moscow%2C%20Kyiv%20has%20said%20that%20it%20expects%20Moscow%20to%20%26quot%3Bunconditionally%26quot%3B%20accept%20a%20ceasefire.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20time%20for%20Russia%20to%20show%20whether%20it%20really%20wants%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukraine's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Andriy%20Sybiga%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoubling%20down%20on%20Moscow's%20conditions%20for%20Kyiv%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe%2C%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20said%20that%20any%20ceasefire%20that%20Russia%20accepts%20will%20only%20benefit%20Ukraine%20as%20his%20troops%20are%20%26quot%3Bsteadily%20advancing%26quot%3B%20through%20Ukrainian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Putin%20has%2C%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Moscow%20will%20never%20accept%20NATO%20troops%20deployed%20as%20peacekeeping%20forces%20in%20Ukraine.%20Russia%20has%20maintainted%20that%20it%20is%20because%20of%20NATO%20coming%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20that%20