0Congress%20Reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20held%20a%20meeting%20today%20to%20finalise%20its%20decision%20to%20link%20Voter%20ID%20cards%20with%20Aadhaar.%20The%20commission's%20move%2C%20the%20Congress%20claimed%2C%20was%20a%20fallout%20of%20its%20complaints%20about%20a%20mismatch%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20in%20Maharashtra%20between%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20now%20warned%20that%20the%20Commission%20should%20ensure%20that%20the%20right%20to%20vote%20of%20a%20single%20eligible%20citizen%20not%20be%20denied%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20breach%20of%20privacy%20of%20any%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20between%20the%20UIDAI%20CEO%2C%20Home%20Secretary%20and%20Law%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20the%20EC%20said%20it%20would%20take%20action%20under%20Article%20326%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%20and%20relevant%20Supreme%20Court%20judgments%2C%20for%20linking%20EPIC%20with%20Aadhaar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20linking%20of%20Aadhar%20with%20electoral%20card%20will%20be%20voluntary.%20Already%2C%2065%20crore%20people%20have%20done%20so%2C%20the%20commission%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20home%20ministry%20will%20work%20with%20the%20EC%20on%20citizenship%20issue%20in%20border%20districts%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20of%20identity.%20The%20Commission%20had%20asked%20the%20ministry%20to%20revert%20on%20how%20the%20issue%20of%20identity%20can%20be%20addressed%20and%20ensure%20genuine%20voters%20are%20allowed%20to%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20upheld%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20law%20but%20struck%20down%20the%20linking%20of%20Aadhaar%20with%20bank%20accounts%20and%20mobile%20connections%20that%20government%20had%20made%20mandatory.%20The%20court%20had%20accepted%20linking%20Aadhaar%20to%20bank%20account%20for%20availing%20government%20subsidies%20and%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnical%20consultations%20between%20UIDAI%20and%20experts%20of%20EC%20will%20begin%20soon%2C%20the%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Article%20326%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20voting%20rights%20can%20only%20be%20given%20to%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%2C%20meaning%20a%20person%20born%20on%20Indian%20soil.%20Aadhaar%20only%20establishes%20the%20identity%20of%20a%20person%20through%20biometrics%20and%20their%20address.%20It%20does%20not%20guarantee%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20remove%20duplicate%20EPIC%20numbers%2C%20the%20Commission%20has%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20lost%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20alleged%20that%20there%20was%20an%20abnormal%20increase%20in%20new%20voters%20enrolled%20in%20just%20five%20months%20between%20the%20Maharashtra%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20had%20implied%20that%20these%20were%20fake%2C%20duplicate%20or%20ghost%20voters.%20Fake%20or%20duplicate%20voters%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20one%20person%20having%20multiple%20voter-ids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20acknowledged%20this%20problem%20of%20'one%20person%20many%20voter-ids'%20raised%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20can%20be%20eliminated%20through%20de-duplication%20using%20Aadhaar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20announced%20it%20will%20link%20Aadhaar%20with%20voter%20IDs.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20parties%20have%20been%20repeatedl