0by%20being%20one%20of%20the%20first%20astronauts%20on%20a%20private%20sector%20spacecraft%2C%20Ms%20Williams%2C%20who%20is%20vastly%20experienced%20and%20also%20held%20the%20record%20for%20the%20maximum%20hours%20of%20spacewalks%20by%20a%20woman%2C%20said%20the%20collaboration%20with%20Boeing%20and%20SpaceX%20had%20been%20really%20good%20and%20the%20companies%20had%20allowed%20them%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20our%20commercial%20partners.%20And%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20really%20good%20collaboration%2C%20a%20really%20good%20partnership%20where%2C%20particularly%20the%20first%20four%20of%20us%20who%20are%20going%20to%20more%20than%20likely%20fly%20on%20their%20spacecraft%2C%20they%20have%20allowed%20us%20into%20their%20companies%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20their%20engineers%20are%20doing%20and%20understand%20from%20the%20grassroots%20part%20of%20development%20of%20the%20spacecraft%2C%20how%20it%20is%20being%20made.%20What's%20interesting%20and%20nice%20about%20that%2C%20I%20think%20they%20are%20open%20to%20that%20because%20both%20of%20these%20companies%20only%20have%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20people%20who%20have%20flown%20in%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20said%20the%20companies%20understood%20that%20the%20astronauts%20were%20trying%20to%20ensure%20they%20would%20be%20successful%20and%20their%20expertise%20would%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20not%20doing%20things%20the%20way%20we%20have%20always%20done%20them.%20We%20are%20letting%20the%20companies%20come%20up%20with%20new%20ideas.%20And%20so%20we%20are%20having%20this%20dialogue%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20debate%2C%20like%2C%20how%20come%20you%20think%20this%20process%20is%20correct%3F%20And%20then%20they%20have%20to%20defend%20it%20a%20little%20bit.%20We%20have%20to%20defend%20our%20ideas%20of%20why%20we%20think%20things%20should%20go%20a%20(certain)%20way.%20And%20then%20we%20could%20come%20to%20the%20best%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20run%20into%20bumps%20and%20have%20a%20little%20heated%20discussion%20on%20some%20of%20these%20things.%20But%20I%20think%20we%20will%20iron%20it%20all%20out%20and%20we%20will%20figure%20it%20all%20out.%20And%20I%20think%20by%20the%20time%20we%20put%20the%20people%20on%20the%20spacecraft%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20very%20safe%20spacecraft%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20Starliner%20project%20in%202018%20and%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20spacecraft%2C%20which%20carried%20her%20and%20fellow%20NASA%20astronaut%20Butch%20Wilmore%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20in%20June%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20Connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Williams'%20father%2C%20Deepak%20Pandya%2C%20is%20from%20Jhulasan%20village%20in%20Gujarat's%20Mehsana%20and%20left%20for%20the%20United%20States%20in%201957.%20The%20Indian%20connection%20was%20clearly%20very%20much%20on%20her%20mind%20when%20NDTV%20asked%20her%20why%20she%20ate%20samosas%20at%20the%20ISS%20and%20said%20she%20had%20asked%20for%20some%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20things%20that%20reminded%20her%20of%20home%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20my%20answer%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20is%2C%20why%20not%3F%20If%20you%20have%20the%20opportunity%2C%20take%20it.%20I%20love%20samosas.%20I%20had%20asked%20for%20some%20special%20things%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20home%2C%20and%20one%20of%20those%20things%20was%20samosas.%20And%20so%20my%20family%20was%20somehow%20able%20to%20work%20with%20NASA%20-%20we%20get%20some%20care%20packages%20when%20we%20are%20up%20in%20space%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20so%20they%20put%20the%20samosas%20in%20there%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20nice%20surprise%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astronaut%20had%20carried%20the%20Gita%20into%20space%20in%20an%20earlier%20mission%20and%20to%20a%20question%20on%20what%20she%20intended%20to%20take%20with%20her%20next%2C%20she%20said%20it%20would%20probably%20be%20a%20Ganesh%20idol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20for%20my%20niece%20and%20nephew%2C%20who%20are%20both%20Indian.%20I%20will%20probably%20bring%20something%20for%20them%2C%20some%20Indian%20toys%20as%20well%20as%20probably%20another%20Ganesh%2C%20because%20Ganesh%20is%20my%20good%20luck%20charm...%20I'm%20more%20of%20a%20just%20a%20spiritual%20person.%20I%20just%20know%20he's%20there%20with%20me%2C%20guiding%20(me)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20also%20said%20she%20had%20been%20good%20friends%20with%20fellow%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Kalpana%20Chawla%20since%20she%20had%20met%20her%20after%20joining%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20together.%20Did%20a%20lot%20of%20nature%20walks%2C%20went%20bike%20riding%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%20just%20talked%20a%20lot.%20She's%20just%20the%20type%20of%20person%20that%20you%20would%20automatically%20connect%20with.%20And%20probably%20our%20similar%20backgrounds%2C%20just%20having%20Indian%20parents%2C%20you%20know%2C%20lent%20itself%20to%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalculated%20Risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20asked%20whether%20Ms%20Chawla's%20death%20-%20when%20the%20Space%20Shuttle%20Columbia%20disintegrated%20during%20reentry%20into%20the%20Earth's%20atmosphere%20in%202003%20-%20worried%20her%20sometimes%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%20and%20no.%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20understood%2C%20I%20knew%20we%20would%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20and%20understand%20exactly%20what%20happened%20to%20Space%20Shuttle%20Columbia.%20And%20we%20would%20fix%20that%20problem.%20And%20moving%20on%20from%20there%2C%20I%20think%20all%20of%20the%20Columbia%20crew%2C%20all%20the%20members%20there%2C%20were%20all%20good%20friends%20of%20ours%20in%20the%20astronaut%20office.%20And%20I%20think%20what%20their%20dream%2C%20their%20vision%2C%20was%20just%20to%20continue%20and%20to%20explore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20so%2C%20it%20worries%20us%20all.%20I%20think%20every%20time%20we%20or%20any%20of%20our%20friends%20from%20the%20office%20get%20on%20a%20rocket%2C%20it's%20a%20big%20explosion%20essentially%20that%20you're%20sitting%20on.%20But%20those%20are%20calculated%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742308560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5fob3eqo_sunita-williams-2016-interview_625x300_18_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fiss-crew-9-boeing-starliner-nasa-spacex-samosas-and-the-risk-of-private-spacecraft-what-sunita-williams-told-ndtv-in-2016-7952828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20years%20before%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20suffered%20glitches%2C%20leaving%20her%20stranded%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20for%20nine%20months%2C%20NDTV%20had%20spoken%20to%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20asked%20whether%20she%20thought%20flying%20on%20a%20privately%20built%20spacecraft%20could%20be%20risky%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fiss-crew-9-boeing-starliner-nasa-spacex-samosas-and-the-risk-of-private-spacecraft-what-sunita-williams-told-ndtv-in-2016-7952828%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Would%20You%20Pay%20Rs%2040000%20for%20Mushrooms%3F%20Why%20Gucchi%20Is%20India%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Expensive%20Fungi!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENestled%20amidst%20the%20breathtaking%20peaks%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20a%20culinary%20treasure%20lies%20hidden%3A%20%3Ca%20rel